{"tid":1391491,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「必要！」香城online最強完全制霸攻略*********","createTime":"2019-07-31T12:39:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T15:56:38.000Z","uid":204565,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aeceaf69ac142c5a2c73348d89ffc4e705e0122b","tid":1391491,"uid":204565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:39:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>大型抗爭對峙(如非必要盡量不要對峙)</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">前排勇武：</span></strong></ins></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">1.盾矛陣(防守用)<br />\n2.油+波子+豆(撤退及阻止速龍用)<br />\n3.速龍埋身必須反擊保護隊友<br />\n4.築路障<br />\n5.將催淚彈掉回敵方</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">中排：</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">1.拉住前排防止前排失去理智<br />\n2.傳遞物資<br />\n3.以遠距離攻擊(Y叉,漆彈,煙花)<br />\n4.帶住前排撤退<br />\n5.用水熄滅催淚彈(嚴禁踢走)</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><ins>後排：</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">1.傳遞物資<br />\n2.保護撤退點<br />\n3.用大聲公呼籲撤退及傳遞資訊<br />\n4.用激光遠攻<br />\n5.受傷急救<br />\n6.收取外界資訊資以判斷形勢</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">高空支援隊：</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n1.利用油漆攻擊(致盲及阻礙敵方前進)<br />\n2.分散敵方注意<br />\n3.分析當前形勢(用通訊軟件傳達)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">*地理位置考慮，前期設路障要諗定點撤退同要保撤退位。</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">小型抗爭</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每區進行快閃(推薦)</span></span></strong></ins><br />\n1.每到每區既黑狗出動次數提高<br />\n2.令到班狗要用埋自己時間又冇得補水<br />\n3.令到班狗唔知邊到係真衝突<br />\n4.當班狗崩潰我地就贏<br />\n5.不同地方設置路障等到班狗出現即撤<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">應對不同狀況</span></span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">速龍應對方法</span></strong></ins></span><br />\n1.放波子or豆同埋油(緩衝)(必須最前線放)<br />\n2.以人數取勝(決不能賣隊友)<br />\n3.一定要反擊(速龍人數唔多)<br />\n4.我地要Y叉遠攻<br />\n5.前排要盾陣同矛(防裝最頂級)<br />\n6.繩挷速龍or牽制速龍or遠程武器<br />\n7.油漆彈or罐(令魔狗致盲喪失攻擊能力)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">*要徹都要等冇速龍既時候</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">應對遠程攻擊</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n1.制用盾陣防禦<br />\n2.以遠程攻擊反擊<br />\n3.人拉人慢慢向後撤退<br />\n4.前排勇武佈波子豆陣(防止速龍突擊)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">水炮車應對方法</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n1.車既體積唔適用於橫街窄巷(尤其中上西環半山區)<br />\n2.車需要在道路上移動<br />\n3.車只有3架<br />\n4.路障已阻檔車既前行<br />\n5.橫街窄巷無法調頭<br />\n6.車既重量會令行駛速度減慢<br />\n7.車駄易受油污影響<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">攻擊策略</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">野貓式攻擊</span></span></strong></ins><br />\n1.多個地邊設置路障<br />\n2.水炮車一到即轉陣地<br />\n3.同時多個地方同時發生衝突，令3車無法同時應對。<br />\n4.守好撤退點<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">反包圍戰術</span></span></strong></ins><br />\n1.同時多方面進攻<br />\n2.以進攻逼使對方陷入我地想要既位置<br />\n3.容易反鎮壓<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港！<br />\n時代革命！</span></div></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果有咩提議各位手足都可以係下面講下幫手推<br />\n希望大家學到點樣同佢地玩<br />\n同意請比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0cf8177effdc081e966345c62cf3f62c442a718","tid":1391491,"uid":204565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:40:16.000Z","msg":"大家前線又好和理非都好，大家都要去同我學下點抗爭，唔好無腦同佢地打，唔想損失任何一個隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd7506b46ce18eb4e605dab3c83964848d32a50c","tid":1391491,"uid":204565,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:40:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBPgk9S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBPgk9S.jpg&h=caa76697&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9cf49682b17b54e13b93254cf8406808dfc9e34f","tid":1391491,"uid":204565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:41:17.000Z","msg":"大家幫手推下"},{"pid":"ee6f5ddf1e9e5a19c4dc08f2ff0d96983d1262a9","tid":1391491,"uid":61520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:41:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">幫公務員們集氣先呀 <br />\n唔該宣傳埋8.2 </div></span></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[推上熱門] 點解8月2號晚 公 務 員 集 會 無 人 講 !!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390038\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390038</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"81bc453e4fd8abbc4f6400b80cd1a42aeac2448a","tid":1391491,"uid":204565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:41:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b2b4d1b0ec2caade62348405771528adfd13519","tid":1391491,"uid":204565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:44:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221470e09ff75e2040bc73a4fd38310165cb1c0b","tid":1391491,"uid":203019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:47:03.000Z","msg":"其中一個建議, 每次速龍衝前我地都閃, 結果有閃唔切隊友被補, 建議出動速龍時, 一係就早D閃, 轉場, 等佢地再佈過陣. 如果堅持唔閃, 速龍衝果陣, 盾陣一定唔可以退, 相反, 第二三排要準備FIGHT BACK, 可以用電筒激光狂照, 警犬見我地唔係好散, 佢地未必真係夠膽衝過黎. 如果佢地照一衝, 前排要有盾擋, 加用竹或遮頭對住佢地. 加埋盾後既攻擊手足進攻. <br />\n當然速龍出擊時多數係放催淚彈, 大家GEAR一定要升級唔好俾催淚彈打散"},{"pid":"045aaa81c53696cb0563af1b0bc1926b73c05fac","tid":1391491,"uid":204565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"221470e09ff75e2040bc73a4fd38310165cb1c0b","tid":1391491,"uid":203019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:47:03.000Z","msg":"其中一個建議, 每次速龍衝前我地都閃, 結果有閃唔切隊友被補, 建議出動速龍時, 一係就早D閃, 轉場, 等佢地再佈過陣. 如果堅持唔閃, 速龍衝果陣, 盾陣一定唔可以退, 相反, 第二三排要準備FIGHT BACK, 可以用電筒激光狂照, 警犬見我地唔係好散, 佢地未必真係夠膽衝過黎. 如果佢地照一衝, 前排要有盾擋, 加用竹或遮頭對住佢地. 加埋盾後既攻擊手足進攻. <br />\n當然速龍出擊時多數係放催淚彈, 大家GEAR一定要升級唔好俾催淚彈打散"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:49:46.000Z","msg":"同意，我上面都有講，要退都要出波子+豆+油去應對速龍，加上盾同矛係冇可能突擊衝擊我地，一係hihi一係比矛插中"},{"pid":"6f5754968642ef4d1a0a4cbbc34d7aa72cb8dc96","tid":1391491,"uid":204565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:50:19.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家幫手推上熱門置頂啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673b3ebb5141ee9c2ae7f1aee6e382d996a33712","tid":1391491,"uid":204565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:09:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d624807dc128624107f5abd983c4d39c342bb89","tid":1391491,"uid":204565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:09:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img